root: ^Helvezia you’re here, how did you know?
^Your mother said you wouldn’t care but here you are, trying to stop me!
^Oh Helvezia you’re making me the happiest man alive right now!
^Whoa there dude, hit the breaks. Either I’m drunk or you are.
^Dear god, your name isn’t Dobo?? I swear I can’t remember every singer I slept with, there are too many of you!
^Yes it is, but I’m not just a singer!
^Yeah yeah I’m sure you have a riveting inner life or whatever but I have actually important shit to talk about.
^No! It’s not about me but who we were to each other!
^You don’t remember anything since your amnesia incident!
^You married me while I had amnesia??
^What the hell, no I did not!
